infographic relation-dagre-flow-tb-badge-card
data
  title DU-high southbound layering
  desc DU-high stays scheduler-agnostic and only speaks canonical IR through the gateway boundary.
  nodes
    - id du
      label ran_du_high
      desc DU-high orchestration
    - id scheduler
      label ran_scheduler_host
      desc Scheduler boundary
    - id fapi
      label ran_fapi_core
      desc Canonical IR and profile negotiation
    - id gateway
      label fapi_rt_gateway
      desc Port sidecar
    - id local
      label local_fapi_profile
      desc Local DU-low backend
    - id aerial
      label aerial_fapi_profile
      desc Future Aerial backend
    - id stub
      label stub_fapi_profile
      desc Contract validation path
  relations
    du -> scheduler
    scheduler -> fapi
    fapi -> gateway
    gateway -> local
    gateway -> aerial
    gateway -> stub
theme
  palette #0f766e #1d4ed8 #0f172a #ea580c #475569 #7c3aed
  base
    text
      font-family Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif
